# Vendored third-party libraries — pinned by SHA, regenerated by
# scripts/download-bosl2.ts. Marking these as vendored+generated tells
# GitHub (linguist) to exclude them from language stats and collapse them
# by default in PR diffs, and signals to Copilot's PR reviewer and other
# code-review tooling that they should not be reviewed.
public/libraries/** linguist-vendored linguist-generated
